OL,5, The boss of the UK's third largest     
OL,6, energy supplier has proposed a plan for
OL,7, the government to subsidise soaring    
OL,8, bills for the poorest households.      
OL,10,FUnder the scheme energy firms could    
OL,11,Fborrow from a government-backed fund,  
OL,12,Fusing the money to subside bills.      
OL,14,FOvo Energy's Stephen Fitzpatrick said  
OL,15,Faction was needed now, or the least    
OL,16,Fwell off would go cold and hungry.     
OL,18,FThe government said it was preparing to
OL,19,Fdeliver any extra support when a new   
OL,20,Fprime minister was in place.           
